  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introdução a Libdrm</title>

    <para>
      <application>Libdrm</application> provides a userspace library for accessing
the direct rendering manager (DRM) on operating systems that support the
ioctl interface. Libdrm is a low-level library, typically used by graphics
drivers such as the Mesa DRI drivers, the X drivers, libva and similar
projects.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

